note: You may not be able to take a train to Cincinnati but you can stay in a train station in Chattanooga. There is some nice hiking nearby in particular the '''Audobon Acres Hiking Trail'''. In Miami, go drink a Cafe Cubano in Little Havana and enjoy the simple life. Atlanta is a city of logos of corporate America: See if you can spot logos for CNN, the olympics,coca cola, Mercede benz, mcdonalds, Wendy's and more..

snippets.text: Back in school, we learnt that temperature drops 6°C every 1,000m and a metre is about three feet. Manitou Springs is at an elevation of 6,412ft and Pike Peak's elevation is 14,110ft – that's 7,698ft more. I did some rough calculations in my head 7,500 / 3 = 2,500m. 2.5 x 6°C = 15°C drop
snippets.title: Pikes Peak was rail impossible in the snow

snippets.text: The Pikes Peak cog railway adventure was fun despite getting stuck in the snow and not reaching the summit. snippets.text: Breakfast is the most important meal of the day and in San Francisco the turnover of restaurants is pretty depressing.
